  "dialogue": {
    "title": "他恐怕去不了",
    "lines": [
      {"speaker": "小雨", "chinese": "今晚你和保罗有空儿的话,我想请你们去看电影。", "pinyin": "Jinwan ni hé Băoluó you kòngr dehuà. wo xiăng qing nimen qù kàn diànying.", "english": "If you and Paulo are free tonight, I'd like to invite you to see a movie."},
      {"speaker": "英男", "chinese": "我不太想去,电影里的对话太快了,我可能听不懂。", "pinyin": "Wỏ bú tài xiăng qù, diànying li de duihuà tài kuài le, wo kěnéng tĩng bu dong.", "english": "I don't really want to go. The dialogue in the movie is too fast. I might not understand."},
      {"speaker": "小雨", "chinese": "有中文字幕,大概的意思你肯定看得懂。", "pinyin": "Yǒu Zhōngwén zìmù, dàgài de yìsi nǐ kěndìng kàn de dǒng.", "english": "There are Chinese subtitles. You can definitely understand the general meaning."},
      {"speaker": "小雨", "chinese": "保罗去得了去不了?", "pinyin": "Báoluo qù de liǎo qù bu liǎo?", "english": "Can Paulo go or not?"},
      {"speaker": "英男", "chinese": "他恐怕去不了。", "pinyin": "Tā kōngpà qù bu liǎo.", "english": "I'm afraid he can't."},
      {"speaker": "小雨", "chinese": "为什么?", "pinyin": "Wèi shénme?", "english": "Why?"},
      {"speaker": "英男", "chinese": "昨天他踢球的时候受伤了,现在走不了路了。", "pinyin": "Zuótiān tã tī qiú de shíhou shòu shang le. xiànzài zou bu lião lù le.", "english": "He got injured while playing football yesterday. He can't walk now."}
    ]
